Russia May Cut Stake in Diamond Miner Alrosa to 50%, RIA Reports

-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 
2011-07-01T12:43:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/russia-may-cut-stake-in-diamond-miner-alrosa-to-50-ria-reports.html
Russia ’s  Finance Ministry  has
proposed cutting the state’s stake in diamond miner OAO Alrosa
to 50 percent in three years, RIA Novosti reported, citing
Deputy Finance Minister Alexei Savatyugin.  The state owns about 91 percent of Alrosa, including stakes
held by regional governments, the company’s website shows. The
Finance Ministry earlier proposed selling a 10 percent stake in
Alrosa, RIA said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Khrennikov in Moscow at 
